{"tid":793093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉刀劈法官枱　工人：要官陪葬","createTime":"2018-08-25T05:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T16:30:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"14a85c12739da2e16491a8dcf76d187da8d66e6c","tid":793093,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:52:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180825/20484270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180825%2F20484270&d=fZWD1M8qUE%2FNkoA38Bw1z2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=bc556813\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180825%2F20484270&h=e47e46f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180825/20484270</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月25日 <br />\n<br />\n涉刀劈法官枱　工人：要官陪葬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180825/large/25la6p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180825%2Flarge%2F25la6p5.jpg&h=01e9949f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裝修工余祖林涉恐嚇法官，昨由囚車押送到法庭應訊。張志華攝 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】裝修工聲稱遭警員打傷，入稟索償但敗訴，其後重審及上訴皆輸。他感有冤無路訴，涉持菜刀闖到判他敗訴的法官陳嘉信席前，揮刀劈枱兼呼喝，揚言自殺亦要陳官陪葬，事後逃走轉頭卻高調自首。案件昨開審，陳官出庭憶述被罵時感百般錯愕，但還未回過神來之際，卻已見男書記率先經職員通道逃跑，陳官此時直覺有危險，「驚驚哋」之下跟隨書記步伐離開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官見書記逃跑感「驚驚哋」<br />\n<br />\n操普通話的被告余祖林（53歲），昨在區域法院否認刑事恐嚇、刑事損壞及藏有攻擊性武器三罪。他沒律師代表，甫出庭便滔滔不絕地向暫委法官蘇文隆申冤，承認曾在高院大樓亮刀，但只為示範「磨脖子、割手腕自殺」；及後他獲悉上訴失敗，才會跑到陳官席前，打算「用生命死在他面前還清白」。<br />\n<br />\n遭恐嚇的主角法官陳嘉信出庭作供，指去年10月17日上午約10時，他正在金鐘高等法院7樓13號法庭就一宗民事案宣讀判詞，其間留意到被告進入法庭，不久便聽到書記關文宇大叫：「你做乜嘢呀？」陳官隨即看見被告向他走近，並以普通話怒罵他。陳官坦言聽不明內容，但對方聲線憤怒且兇惡。<br />\n<br />\n陳官直言從未見過有人在庭上大聲呼喝及怒罵法官，感到錯愕，但還未回過神來，便「見到我個書記係我面前跑到去職員通道，離開法庭」。雖然陳官不知道書記為何速逃，但見狀直覺有危險，感到「驚驚哋」，於是「都走埋出去」。<br />\n<br />\n庭上播放當日法庭錄音，先聽到書記呼喊「等等」，接着被告大叫「陳嘉信，我找到你，你以為我找不到你？你他媽的，我斬死你&hellip;&hellip;」。被告昨對此直認不諱，但強調自己聲量不大。<br />\n<br />\n被告親自盤問陳官，自言當日說出所謂恐嚇字句時，陳官已離開法庭；陳官不同意，強調確聽到被告呼喝怒罵，但同意自己在怒罵聲中離開。被告又重申當日只欲在陳官面前自殺，無奈「我想在他面前自殺，他走了，我自殺不了嘛」。案件周一續審，被告還柙。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC1163/17<br />\n■記者楊思雅  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n教授稱一氧化碳滅鼠　 印傭：家無鼠蹤<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n買「波子」逃稅72萬　消防判囚"},{"pid":"607f9cf5d249d79b0b2f7bf494cee83c21adb80d","tid":793093,"uid":14262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/135415_efcce9e4796cad194ad1b448c3ec6c40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F135415_efcce9e4796cad194ad1b448c3ec6c40.png&h=c74b573a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ea791a555dea9ef24e110950adaf172ff5b119f","tid":793093,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"書記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1643b057a6928d2f02bf0a99fa0af99c84d52455","tid":793093,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5ea791a555dea9ef24e110950adaf172ff5b119f","tid":793093,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"書記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T06:20:21.000Z","msg":"打工仔黎渣"},{"pid":"f9e8d6c9f4f959368de43568ca7efba5561bb6cd","tid":793093,"uid":166886,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T06:23:25.000Z","msg":"仆街，操普通話vs法官<br />\n好難揀俾咩皮"},{"pid":"36c84765d4bf2254201846e39b309b8ae033cfa3","tid":793093,"uid":176166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1cc0d45bff577229e8cb1922d49768c4563746d","tid":793093,"uid":119230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T06:47:22.000Z","msg":"就係佢搞到每次去high court 都要security check <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e697620b2cb4c0dcd2e528e5317fa49d7a597467","tid":793093,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:21:26.000Z","msg":"死大陸喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e491dbc78e1616188ba6d24c8aab96babef18569","tid":793093,"uid":167441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:01:13.000Z","msg":"香港要冠啲呢啲人"},{"pid":"cea97fe98cad17dd08ad3aab29d71fcc885f1e6e","tid":793093,"uid":167441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e491dbc78e1616188ba6d24c8aab96babef18569","tid":793093,"uid":167441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:01:13.000Z","msg":"香港要冠啲呢啲人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"香港要多啲呢啲人"},{"pid":"f3cc22dfcc651ac3b8bacd2832abaee1a29b2f1c","tid":793093,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IRZhCH7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIRZhCH7.gif&h=d6786683&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fca377cd4cb2d89b875c32b10f2713b2ed383da","tid":793093,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1643b057a6928d2f02bf0a99fa0af99c84d52455","tid":793093,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5ea791a555dea9ef24e110950adaf172ff5b119f","tid":793093,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"書記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T06:20:21.000Z","msg":"打工仔黎渣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"我唔撈喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a429d9aaa6131492fb21b986ed767963b7927a","tid":793093,"uid":864